('4003', 'Anchor Bolt Plan', 'A plan detailing the position, sizes, etc of anchor bolts required for anchoring the structures/equipment to the foundations.  3D information may be extracted and issued in 2D format as a document or may alternatively be extracted from the 3D model directly by the viewer.  In the context of Onshore,  this document type is for civil discipline use only. For an offshore structural discipline GA that could also show anchor bolts, doc type 4018 would be used.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'CA', 'Civil', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 55),
('4006', 'Architecture Drawing', 'A drawing of an architectural nature.  Includes floor plans, room layouts, reflected ceiling plans, etc.  3D information may be extracted and issued in 2D format as a document or may alternatively be extracted from the 3D model directly by the viewer.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'CA', 'Civil', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 56),
('4009', 'Bar Bending Schedule', 'A document detailing the sizes, numbers, mark references and bending dimensions of all reinforcing bars in a concrete element.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'CA', 'Civil', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 57),
('4012', 'Concrete Detail Drawing', 'A detailed drawing (e.g. plan, section and/or detail views) of a concrete element, such as a foundation, a wall, a slab, a beam, etc., to a suitable scale.  3D information may be extracted and issued in 2D format as a document or may alternatively be extracted from the 3D model directly by the viewer.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'CA', 'Civil', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 58),
('4015', 'Earthworks Drawing', 'A drawing showing cut and fill profiles and other details for site earthworks. 3D information may be extracted and issued in 2D format as a document or may alternatively be extracted from the 3D model directly by the viewer.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'CA', 'Civil', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 59),
('4018', 'General Arrangement Diagram', 'A diagram showing the main features and locations of major items. Usually has some dimensions to convey spatial relationships but is generally inadequate for construction.   Architectural: Sometimes includes layouts of all rooms including equipment and accommodation, external layouts and elevations.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'CA', 'Civil', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 60),
('4021', 'Piling Plan', 'A plan showing the position and details of the piles required for the foundations.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'CA', 'Civil', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 61),
('4024', 'Road Layout Drawing', 'A drawing showing the layout and details for site roads.  3D information may be extracted and issued in 2D format as a document or may alternatively be extracted from the 3D model directly by the viewer.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'CA', 'Civil', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 62),
