('4069', 'Isometric Drawing', 'A 3D dimensional representation of piping. Shows relevant piping data such as materials, wall thickness, weld details and positions, elevation heights, etc. May show stress points. 3D information may be extracted and issued in 2D format as a document or may alternatively be extracted from the 3D model directly by the viewer.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'LA', 'Piping', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 325),
('4072', 'Piping Arrangement Drawing', 'A piping drawing, usually in plan/elevation format, showing the routing and physical arrangement of pipes within a given area/building. Shows relevant piping data such as materials, wall thickness, connection details, support locations, etc.  3D information may be extracted and issued in 2D format as a document or may alternatively be extracted from the 3D model directly by the viewer.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'LA', 'Piping', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 326),
('4075', 'Process and Instrumentation Diagram', 'PandID - A diagram that shows all the relevant process and control information for each system using symbols and lines to represent equipment, piping, instrumentation, control devices, control philosophy/strategy and significant services. It is considered to be the master document to be used during Construction and Operation.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'LA', 'Piping', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 327),
('4078', 'Process Flow Diagram', 'PFD - A diagram used to define the process for a facility. There are many process/piping parameters listed on the PFD such as process flows, compositions, pressures and temperatures for each significant process and utility stream and for each operating case. Also called: Heat and Material Balance (H and MB, HMB), Process Scheme (PS).', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'LA', 'Piping', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 328),
('4080', 'Other Drawing', NULL, 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'LA', 'Piping', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 329),
('4301', 'Action List', 'Includes Punch List.', NULL, NULL, 'LA', 'Piping', 'IFI, AFU, AFP, AFT', true, 330),
('4324', 'Line List', 'A tabulation listing all (piping) lines within a project scope, with corresponding characteristics (sizes, materials, design data, insulation requirements, test requirements, etc).', NULL, NULL, 'LA', 'Piping', 'IFI, AFU, AFP, AFT', true, 331),
('4327', 'Valve Summary List', 'A tabulation listing the main data (e.g. types, pressure ratings, end connections, trim requirements, operators, accessories, etc.) applicable to each (piping) valve within the project scope, usually on a one line per item basis. Sometimes a valve is so important it needs a separate specification.', NULL, NULL, 'LA', 'Piping', 'IFI, AFU, AFP, AFT', true, 332),
