('5503', 'Design Basis', 'Overall design basis and criteria for a project is called Design Basis Memorandum, whereas the one defined for a specific (sub)-discipline is the Discipline Design Basis._x000D_ Synonyms: Design Criteria, Design Basis Memorandum, Discipline Design Basis, Design Basis of Estimate (DBOE), Basis of Design (BOD), Discipline Design Criteria, Process Design Basis.', NULL, NULL, 'PA', 'Process', 'IFI, AFU, AFP, AFT', true, 526),
