('6612', 'Equipment Register', 'A register/database containing all pertinent data about equipment that is installed on the facility. Frequently referred to as the CMMS (Computerised Maintenance Management System). Refer to the EPC/IM Contract Scope of Work (the EXHIBIT-G, section 5.3 / 5.4 / 5.5 for more detail). Includes Equipment Database, Summary Equipment Database, Approved Equipment List etc.  For Project Material Master data list use doc type 6680.', NULL, NULL, 'PA', 'Process', 'IFI, AFU, AFP, AFT', true, 531),
