('4066', 'Control System Architecture Drawing', 'High-level drawing showing the main components and the configuration of the control system in a facility/project: PLC, DCS, SCADA, Communication, ESD, PSD, FGS, etc. It shows device counts, networks, protocols, hardware/servers, workstations, etc.', 'Tier 1', 'RLMU', 'TA', 'Telecom', 'ASB, AFC, AFU, AFD', true, 651),
