('4333', 'Index Of Documents', 'Previously known as Book Index / Register of Books (before 2011). This doc type classifies specific indexes related to a combination of individual documents (hereinafter called books or manuals). Some examples of books include: Inspection Test Plans (ITP), Operating Manual, Maintenance Manual, Piping Material Specifications, Instrument Data Sheets.  This doc type shall also be used to classify any document that constitutes a record of information about all documents in a project(s), providing a single point of reference for the identification, location and status of a document (previously known as Master Document Register or MDR).', NULL, NULL, 'VA', 'Information Management', 'IFI, AFU, AFP, AFT', true, 723),
