('8215', 'Safety Case', 'A document produced by the operator describing the SMS. This requires the formal identification of the hazards and risks; the measures taken to reduce the identified risks to a level that is As Low As Reasonably Practicable; and the Safety Management System to ensure the implementation and compliance of risk reduction measures.', NULL, NULL, 'H02', 'Process Safety', 'IFI, AFU, AFP, AFT', true, 1135),
