('7753', 'Terms Of Reference', 'Specifies the scope and details of the activity to which it refers and any conditions relating to the appointment of a person(s) to undertake the activity (usually used in relation to the supply of professional services). It recalls the background and specifies the scope of the evaluation, states the main motives for an evaluation and the questions asked. It sums up available knowledge and outlines an evaluation method and describes the distribution of work, schedule and the responsibilities among the people participating in an evaluation process.', NULL, NULL, 'FA', 'Cost and Planning', 'IFI, AFU, AFP, AFT', true, 1222),
